[b]Description[/b]
ORANGE DIARY PRO

Journal + Notepad + Organizer

Orange Diary is an easy-to-use daily journal app that helps you organize all your ideas and information in your phone. Orange Diary lets you take journal entries, capture photos, create to-do lists, record voice, etc ....
